title.rendered: Pack of 12, Sentry Medicrepe Elastic Heavy Crepe Bandage 5cm x 1.5m Unstretched

content.rendered:
The Medicrepe® (Elastic Crepe Bandage) Heavy range is constructed from a blend of cotton and polyurethane fibres (spandex), giving excellent stretch and memory, with overlocked fast edges. Conforms to BP standards.

These bandages are

  •  washable
  •  cost effective

Ideal for:

  • strong support bandaging
